\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:tangent-vector"

\end_inset

 相比，我们看到它映射到局部坐标 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

，如下所示：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\yhat=\frac{1-\exp(-ad_{\xihat})}{ad_{\xihat}}\hat{x}
\]

\end_inset

这可被用来构造雅可比矩阵 
\begin_inset Formula $f'(\xi)$
\end_inset

